# Cloudflare Pages Redirects Configuration
# Ensure llms.json and llms.txt are served directly

/llms.txt    /llms.txt    200
/llms.json   /llms.json   200

# SPA fallback for React Router
/*    /index.html   200

# NOTE: Domain-level redirect (arif.fazil → arif-fazil.com) is NOT possible
# from this file — _redirects handles path-level only. The proper fix is at
# the registrar (Namecheap/Porkbun/etc.) or via a Cloudflare Worker that
# inspects request.host. The SPA itself has a JS guard in index.html that
# detects window.location.hostname === 'arif.fazil' and redirects.
